@startuml

state "Waiting for User Action" as Initial [*]

Initial --> AddNewGood : add new goods to inventory
AddNewGood --> UpdatePrice : update price of existing items
UpdatePrice --> RemoveGoods : remove goods from inventory
RemoveGoods --> ExpireCheck : identify expired goods and notify user
ExpireCheck --> PlaceOrder : place order for additional goods when required
PlaceOrder --> GenerateInvoice : generate invoice for the order once placed
GenerateInvoice --> SearchItems : search for items available in inventory and select them for purchase
SearchItems --> CalculateDiscount : calculate applicable discount and tax based on selected items
CalculateDiscount --> GenerateReceipt : generate receipt for the customer after the purchase
GenerateReceipt --> ReplaceOrCancel : allow user to replace an item or cancel the receipt during billing process
ReplaceOrCancel --> RecordRequests : record customer requests for items that may not be currently available
RecordRequests --> SummaryReport : view a summary report of all transactions carried out in the system at any point

@enduml
